OL,3,CHow a #12 makeup brush is helping to
OL,4,Crestore this historic Opera House
OL,6,FSpecialist Decorations Manager Natasha
OL,7,FBeharrell has also found a cost-
OL,8,Fcutting way to apply the leaf by using
OL,9,Fa #12 makeup brush.
OL,11,FShe said: "If this was real gold, we'd
OL,12,Fbe very gently polishing it in but
OL,13,Fbecause it's Dutch, we need to iron
OL,14,Fout the creases so you need something
OL,15,Fmore compact.
OL,17,F"It's been a really pleasurable
OL,18,Fexperience."
