OL,4,Crestore this historic Opera House
OL,6,FThe team aim to finish applying the
OL,7,Fleaf to the ceiling by the end of
OL,8,FFebruary.
OL,10,FWork will then move on to colouring
OL,11,Fthe walls and marbling columns, as
OL,12,Fwell as applying more gilding to the
OL,13,Fbalconies.
OL,15,FGilder Kevin Ruggeri said: "It's very
OL,16,Fexciting working on such a big project
OL,17,Flike this and being part of the
OL,18,Frestoration of a historic building."
